# Inheritance

The passing of properties and methods from parent class to child class is called Inheritance.
Note: I can't pass/use the constructor function of parent class in child class. it is just calleable within the class in which it is defined.
## Types of Inheritance:
1- Single Level Inheritance
2- Hybrid Inheritance
3- Multi Level Inheritance
4- Sibling Inheritance.



